in-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">“大家好呀，欢迎来到我们的科普小课堂！今天我带来了一个有趣的谜语想考考大家。谜语是这样的：‘皮儿黄，身子长，营养丰富味道香。能做爆米花和粥，你们常吃啥粮食？’小朋友们，猜猜这是什么呢？请举手告诉我！没错，谜底就是玉米！今天我们就要一起开启一段神奇的旅程，探索‘玉米的奇幻之旅’！准备好了吗？让我们一起出发吧！”</p> \n<hr data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: 1px;\"> \n<h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: block;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(14, 136, 235); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: bold; display: block;\">幻灯片2：谜语开场</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h3> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">“在我们开始之前，我想和大家分享这个谜语，因为它和我们今天的主题有很大的关系哦！你们猜到了吗？就是玉米！看，这里有一只可爱的玉米卡通形象，它准备和我们一起冒险！”</p> \n<hr data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: 1px;\"> \n<h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: block;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(14, 136, 235); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: bold; display: block;\">幻灯片3：玉米的古老历史</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h3> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">“现在我们来聊聊玉米的古老故事！玉米可是有着9000年的悠久历史呢！它最早是在美洲被古代墨西哥的印第安人种植的。科学家们通过考古发现，玉米的祖先其实是一种叫做大刍草的植物。看看这幅图，想象一下古代墨西哥人种玉米的样子，那一定非常有趣！”</p> \n<hr data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 10px; margin-bottom: 10px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; border-top-style: solid; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: 1px;\"> \n<h3 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; display: block;\"><span class=\"prefix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span><span class=\"content\" style=\"font-size: 18px; color: rgb(14, 136, 235); line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; font-weight: bold; display: block;\">幻灯片4：玉米是如何改变的？</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h3> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 8px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">“接下来，我们来看看玉米是如何变化的！从最初的野生植物，到现在我们吃的美味玉米，变化可大了！现代的玉米颗粒不仅更大，味道还更甜哦，产量也增加了！看这幅图，左边是野生玉米，右边是现代玉米，小朋友们，你们更喜欢哪种呢？”</p> \n<hr data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: